						<summary>

						<p>On the lintel of the entrance into the Vallabharāyasvāmi temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1555, Sarvadhāri, Phālguṇa śu. 15, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record some gift to the temple of Śrīvallabharāya by Sū • • • parinedu of Kētanapalli.</p>						

